T02D2161:256a-1: n'i l'am ba ra dha ra badzra p'a ni ho ma bi dhi n'a ma /
T02D2161:256a-3: phyag na rdo rje gos sngon po can gyi sbyin sreg gi cho ga zhes bya ba /
T02D2161:256a-4: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2161:256a-5: gang zhig med par de mi 'byung //
T02D2161:256a-6: des na de la 'jug pa brtsam //
T02D2161:256a-7: de la 'dir thab khung gru gsum pa mgo lhor bstan pa'i nang du /
T02D2161:256a-8: khro bo'i rdo rje sor brgyad pa bkod de /
T02D2161:256a-9: thal ba dang sol bas nag por byugs la dri
T02D2161:256a-10: chu dang bong bu dang rnga mo'i rtug pas byug
T02D2161:256a-11: par bya'o // der mgal dum mam /
T02D2161:256a-17: me tog nag po ni mchod yon no //
T02D2161:256a-21: bdud rtsi lnga sbyar ba'i spos so //
T02D2161:256a-23: dri chu dang til nag po sbyar ba ni dri chab /
T02D2161:256a-24: dri chen dang mi sha bsres pa'i lha bshos te /
T02D2161:256a-25: de rnams g-yas su gzhag par bya'o //
T02D2161:256b-1: bdud rtsi lnga dang bsres pa'i yungs mar rnams ni
T02D2161:256b-2: dgang gzar du blugs te khrag tu byas la dbul
T02D2161:256b-3: lo // shing tsher ma can gyi yam shing dang /
T02D2161:256b-16: bya rog gi sha rnams dang /
T02D2161:256b-18: rnga mo'i rtug pa rnams ni sreg rdzas te /
T02D2161:256b-19: sha dang rus par bsam mo //
T02D2161:256b-21: rang lha'i rnal 'byor byas la rdzas byin gyis brlabs nas bgegs bskrad do //
T02D2161:256b-23: sme sha can nam rdo las byung ba'am /
T02D2161:256b-26: aom badzra p'a ni ma h'a kro dha dzv'a la
T02D2161:256b-27: dzva'a la h'um h'um h'um phat phat phat sv'a h'a
T02D2161:256b-29: me 'bar ba'i nang du ram las thab khung bskyed
T02D2161:256b-30: la de'i nang du h'um las nyi ma'i steng du
T02D2161:256b-31: aom a'a h'um las 'khor lo dang /
T02D2161:256b-34: de nas khro bo'i me lha shin tu khros pa /
T02D2161:256b-35: skra kham pa gyen du brdzes pa /
T02D2161:256b-36: 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro ba /
T02D2161:256b-38: g-yas na rdo rje dang skyabs sbyin /
T02D2161:256b-39: g-yon na dril bu dang dbyug pa /
T02D2161:256b-40: ram las me dang rlung gi dkyil 'khor la bsams te /
T02D2161:256b-41: ye shes sems dpa' dgug pa dang /
T02D2161:256b-44: dbang du byas nas der byin rlabs dang /
T02D2161:256b-46: khrus gsol nas zhal gdangs pa'i nang du mchod rdzas dang sreg rdzas rnams 'dis dbul te /
T02D2161:256b-47: aom badzra p'a ni ma h'u bh'u ta dzv'a la
T02D2161:256b-48: ya sarba bhasmim ku ru sarba dusht'am ma ma che
T02D2161:256b-49: ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat ces pas gsad
T02D2161:256b-50: par bya'o // de nas me 'bar bas rgyur gyur pa'am /
T02D2161:256b-51: yang na de'i snying gar dpal phyag na rdo rje
T02D2161:256b-52: gos sngon po can sgrub thabs las ji skad gsungs
T02D2161:256b-53: pa bzhin nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas par bskyed
T02D2161:256b-54: nas ye shes sems dpa' snga ma bzhin bstims la
T02D2161:256b-55: / de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang bskur bar bya'o //
T02D2161:256b-56: de nas phreng ba'i sngags la m'a ra ya dang
T02D2161:256b-57: bcas pas mchod rdzas snga ma bzhin du dbul lo
T02D2161:257a-3: rdzas lhag ma rnams me lha la phul nas /
T02D2161:257a-4: aom bdag dang gzhan gyi don rnams ni //
T02D2161:257a-5: bsgrubs te sbyin sreg bzhes nas kyang //
T02D2161:257a-6: slar yang 'byon par mdzad nas kyang //
T02D2161:257a-7: bdag la sngags kyi dngos grub stsol //
T02D2161:257a-8: zhes me lha gshegs su gsol lo //
T02D2161:257a-9: de'i rjes su dam tshig pa rang la bsdus te /
T02D2161:257a-11: nyung bar 'dod na bla ma'i zhal nas ji skad gsungs pa bzhin du 'di la 'jug par bya'o //
T02D2161:257a-12: phyag na rdo rje'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga mdor
T02D2161:257a-13: bsdus pa zhes bya ba nam gru'i rigs las byung
T02D2161:257a-14: ba dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon dz'a ba ri
T02D2161:257a-17: // / ba la po'i pandi ta de ba p'u rna ma ti dang /
